In backend/, create main.py.
Define a FastAPI app with two endpoints:

POST /analyze — accepts JSON body {github_url: str}.
Runs ingestion → parsing → embedding → agent as background steps.
Streams progress via SSE using sse-starlette, emitting events:
  {event: "progress", data: "Cloning repo..."}
  {event: "progress", data: "Parsing N files..."}
  {event: "progress", data: "Embedding chunks..."}
  {event: "progress", data: "Running analysis..."}
  {event: "done", data: <ReportJSON as JSON string>}
Store the completed report in an in-memory dict keyed by a uuid job_id.
Return the job_id immediately as part of the SSE stream header (first event).

GET /report/{job_id} — returns the stored ReportJSON as JSON.

Add CORS middleware allowing all origins for local dev.

